cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language processing and specifically focuses on automatic image captioning and quality estimation of captions. 
2. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is also a likely category as the paper deals with image captioning and uses images as input. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another likely category as the paper deals with machine learning models for caption generation and quality estimation. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper deals with designing and experimenting with different modeling approaches for quality estimation. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with image-caption pairs and their quality estimation.
